holiday-melvin-gregg-miss-lawrence-1202750512/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。戴表演表演资历浅，丹尼尔斯担心她能否胜任该角色，但是她的表演教练给他发去一段iPhone视频，展示她的演技，打消了他的疑虑<ref name=Keegan-Jan2021>{{cite news |url= https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/united-states-vs-billie-holiday |title= In 'The United States vs Billie Holiday,' Lee Daniels Tackles the Untold Story of the Jazz Singer's Civil Rights Activism |last= Keegan |first= Rebecca |date= 2021-01-11 |work= The Hollywood Reporter |access-date= 2021-02-19 |archive-date= 2021-02-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210220013700/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/united-states-vs-billie-holiday |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

影片于2019年10月6日在蒙特利尔开拍<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.iheartradio.ca/news/andra-day-in-montreal-to-star-in-billie-holiday-biopic-1.9965658 |title=Andra Day In Montreal To Star In Billie Holiday Biopic |last=Kennedy |first=John R. |date=2019-09-16 |website=IHeartRadio |access-date=2019-10-27 |archive-date=2019-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002212737/https://www.iheartradio.ca/news/andra-day-in-montreal-to-star-in-billie-holiday-biopic-1.9965658 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

