== 评价 ==
=== 收视率 ===
Hulu称影片上线首三天成为观看人数最多的作品，{{tsl|en|Samba TV|Samba TV}}估计影片美国收视率达28.7万<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2021-03-02|url= https://deadline.com/2021/03/hulu-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-weekend-viewership-1234705203/ |title= Hulu's 'The United States Vs. Billie Holiday' Tops Streamer's Weekend Movies Amid Star Andra Day's Golden Globes Win |website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2021-03-02}}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[爛番茄|爛番茄]]收录158条评论，平均得分5.4/10，网站共识写道：“尽管《美国诉比莉·哈乐黛》对主题超然性的表述暧昧，安德拉·戴的表演还是很聪明地弥补了这点不足之处<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_united_states_vs_billie_holiday|title=The United States vs. Billie Holiday (2021)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|access-date=2021-03-29|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215233509/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_united_states_vs_billie_holiday|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录43条评论，平均得分52/100，表示“褒贬不一或口碑平平”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday|title=The United States vs. Billie Holiday Reviews|website=Metacritic|access-date=2021-03-29|archive-date=2021-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221231515/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》的大卫·鲁尼认为：“戴让人甚为陶醉，在缺乏有力连接线索的情况下，为各部分安排了精彩的地方，即便李·丹尼尔斯这部笨拙的传记剧情片，因为风格的不一致和叙事的不足而脱线。这部作品很糟糕，尽管在主角出离愤怒的表演下，也有吸引人的一面，但是显得粗糙、脆弱<ref>{{cite web|last=Rooney|first=David|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-film-review|title='The United States vs Billie Holiday': Film Review|website=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2021-02-19|access-date=2021-02-19|archive-date=2021-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219170359/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-film-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》的{{tsl|en|Owen Gleiberman|欧文·格里伯曼}}赞扬戴的演技：“在这部无规则延伸、撕裂，但在情感上有点反复无常、背景设在哈乐黛人生最后一年的这部传记片中，戴赋予比莉珍珠般灿烂的声音。这般声音随时间变化，变得粗犷、坚硬，我们在比莉身上同样能看到这种演变<ref>{{Cite web|last=Gleiberman|first=Owen|date=2021-02-19|title='The United States vs. Billie Holiday' Review: Scattered but Scorching, and a Must-See for Andra Day's Performance|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/reviews/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-review-andra-day-lee-daniels-1234908289/|access-date=2021-02-19|work=Variety|archive-date=2021-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219170240/https://variety.com/2021/film/reviews/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-review-andra-day-lee-daniels-1234908289/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

《[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]》的彼特·哈蒙德（Pete Hammond）认为：“对于戴的表演，你简直不能挑剔太多，尤其是对她这位首次亮相的演员。她能捕捉到哈乐黛的神韵，以及这位受压迫的艺术家的原始、真诚一面，展现出她认为艺术和天赋能让世界更加公平的信念<ref>{{Cite news |url= https://deadline.com/video/united-states-vs-billie-holiday-review-andra-day-lee-daniels/ |title= 'The United States Vs. Billie Holiday' Review: Andra Day Soars In Lee Daniels' Compelling True Story Of Feds Targeting Of Great Singer |work= Deadline Hollywood |first= Pete |last= Hammond |date= 2021-02-19 |access-date= 2021-02-22 |archive-date= 2021-02-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210220022554/https://deadline.com/video/united-states-vs-billie-holiday-review-andra-day-lee-daniels/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”《[[卫报|卫报]]》的彼得·布拉德肖（Peter Bradshaw）给出2/5星的评价，认为：“戴的演绎发自肺腑，但导演和剧情费劲，缺乏丹尼尔斯之前作品《[[天生不是寶貝|天生不是寶貝]]》（2009）和《{{tsl|en|The Paperboy (2012 film)|送报男孩}}》（2012）中的神气和不准确。影片笼罩着庄严、敬仰的氛围，但直接被音乐本身消除<ref>{{cite news|last=Bradshaw|first=Peter|date=2021-02-19|title=The United States vs Billie Holiday review – Lee Daniels' misguided biopic|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/feb/19/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-review-lee-daniels-misguided-biopic|access-date=2021-02-19|archive-date=2021-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219170617/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2021/feb/19/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-review-lee-daniels-misguided-biopic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《DiscussingFilm》打出3/5星的评分，认为戴的表演是这部本该令人难忘但胡乱的影片中，唯一让人难忘的部分<ref>{{cite web |last1=Wade |first1=A. Felicia |title='The United States vs. Billie Holiday' Review – Andra Day Shines in a Muddled Mess |url=https://discussingfilm.net/2021/02/26/the-united-states-vs-billie-holiday-review-andra-day-shines-in-a-muddled-mess/ |website=DiscussingFilm |access-date=2021-03-05}}</ref>。

